## 💡 Current Performance Metrics

**Target response times:**

- GET /api/cart: < 500ms
- GET /api/ingredients: < 300ms (with cache: 50-100ms)
- GET /api/stories: < 500ms
- GET /: < 2000ms (SSR)
- GET /product/[id]: < 800ms

**If slower - optimize!**

